            <a href="/restaurant/orders" onclick="dismissOrderNotif()" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;background:#f97316;color:#fff;border:none;border-radius:8px;font-weight:700;font-size:.82rem;padding:.35rem 1rem;text-decoration:none;flex-shrink:0;">
                🧾 Vezi comenzile
